The charity fund department is the place for patients who couldn't afford the hospital bill while carrying too much of a disease to move out from the doctors's watch.[p]
They're usually on the last of the checklist among doctors and nurses, espcially at busy days.[p]
I arrive at the charity fund department with Kai while he introduces me as the new personal nurse at this place[p]
[_tb_end_text]

