#Middle age woman
Dr Quang, what are you trying to do sending that girl to us?[p]
You think we don't hear all the rumours about her?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[chara_mod  name="An"  time="600"  cross="true"  storage="chara/1/An_concern.png"  ]
