The patient's cut is stink with worms and maggots, makes even other patients turning away. This must be due to the lateness of turning into the hospital too late.[p]
I treat his wound with antibiotic while trying to convince him to book an operation. He harshly denies, probably because he couldn't afford the bill.[p]
Not giving up, i spend an hour explaining all the options he has with charity fund, insurance,...while treating his wound. [p]
How come i'm the only active nurse in this place?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

